data.name: WelcomeBody
data.value: Attack Surface Analyzer catalogues the changes made to an operating system attack surface by the installation of new software. ASA can be used to take a snapshot of your system state before and after the installation of product(s) and displays the changes made to a number of key elements of the system attack surface allowing you to see what attack surfaces may be exposed after installation of the target product(s). ASA was developed by Microsoft.
